node.text:
Fall in love with Sicily at the Grand Hotel Timeo with @ananewyork. 💗 The property sits atop Sicilian cliffs with breathtaking views of Mount Etna, a Greek amphitheater, and the terracotta rooftops of Taormina.

Feel like royalty in their gorgeous rooms and luxurious villas, indulge in Sicilian cuisine, and give yourself a moment to rediscover Sicily as experienced by the world's greatest artists, writers, and European aristocracy. 😍

💡 BH Tip: Want to see Mount Etna up close? The hotel offers boat excursions and tours of the volcano! If you're more of a history buff, head to the Teatro Antico Di Taormina by foot just a few steps from the hotel. 🎭

When was your last trip to Sicily? Is Italy on your bucket list? 🇮🇹

📸 @ananewyork
📍 @belmondgrandhoteltimeo, Sicily, Italy

Swimming in mid-air with @hobopeeba. 😎 Connecting both Embassy Gardens and Legacy Building, this world-famous London attraction has captured the world's attention as the first ever Sky Pool with gorgeous, unobstructed views of the city. 🏙

The Embassy Gardens is your access to the Sky Pool, as well as The Orangery and Sky Deck. These rooftop destinations give tenants and their guests a place to unwind, socialize and work in one of the poshest places in London! 

💡BH Tip: While the Sky Pool is truly a marvel you may want to experience, it is highly exclusive for Embassy Gardens tenants and their guests. Best to make friends here and there, yes? 😉

Would you take a dip here? 💦 Share with us your most beautiful memory of London!

📽 @hobopeeba
📍 @embassygardens, London, England

node.text:
This is Amanruya: idyllic, chic, and a break from the usual. Imagine strolling in a village-like property, with the scent of pine trees melding with the Aegean sea breeze. ✨

Craving Turkish and Mediterranean meals made from locally sourced ingredients? Decide if you'll be enjoying it poolside, by the beach, in their Anatolian dining pavilion, or in the comfort of your own room! You can never run out of choices here. 😎

If you're the type to go all-in for wellness, Amanruya will definitely give you the most amazing pampering with unforgettable views! Think massages and mani-pedis overlooking the sea. 💅🏼 Ever had pampering with views of the sea? Would you want to experience that in Amanruya? 💆🏼

📍 @amanruya, Bodrum, Turkey

Don't you love this romantic setup from @momentsofgregory? 😍 Amp up the mood at Bill & Coo Suites and Lounge with a sunset dinner poolside. Catch feelings while watching the Mykonos sunset at the in-suite deck with your significant other! 

Make sure to plan an unforgettable staycation at Bill & Coo before your trip! The staff will be more than happy to help you create a memory that will last forever. Who knows, you just might open a new chapter. 🥂

Have you visited Mykonos? Would you want to stay here? 

📽️ @momentsofgregory
📍 @billandcoowayoflife, Mykonos, Greece
🎶 Jay Finesse feat. Laywap - Myboo

node.text:
With its Andalusian architecture and Mediterranean elegance, Finca Cortesin gives you an experience of overall luxury you can't forget.✨ You might never want to leave once you stay in their spacious rooms, strolled at their manicured gardens, had a round of golf at their exclusive golf course, and had a cocktail at their beach club, but that's understandable! 😉

Feel the country club vibe while you swipe to see why Finca Cortesin is a dream destination in Spain. It's not hard to imagine yourself there now. Maybe it's time to book a holiday there? ✈️
 
📍 @fincacortesin, Casares, Spain

With their exclusive rooms, jacuzzi, and private pool, there will be no distractions as you and your loved one can focus on falling in love all over again. ❤️

Honeymoon? Proposal? Or just a vacation for two? Let love guide you to this gorgeous honeymoon destination overlooking the sea! 🇹🇷

Would you bring your loved one here? When was the last time you and your partner went on a trip? 💋

📽️ @bugunnereyegidelim

node.text:
Eco-glamping with a little razzle-dazzle with @c_a_b_i_n_s_e_e_k_e_r_s at the Leadwood Safari Company. 🇿🇦 Rustic luxuries are offered by the camp located within the Dinokeng Big 5 Game Reserve with amenities that will make you feel at home. Eager to create a different kind of adventure? Your tent is your starting point to experience what the African wilderness has to offer!

💡 BH Tip: Book a game drive! Ask the staff for daily drive schedules for a unique, outdoor activity! Wildlife photographers and bird enthusiasts, this is highly recommended for your itinerary!

Is glamping a part of your travel experience? Would you stay here? 😎
 
📸 @c_a_b_i_n_s_e_e_k_e_r_s
📍 @leadwoodsafaricompany, Dinokeng Game Reserve, South Africa

node.text:
Aesthetic feels brought to you by @admbrs. 😍 Experience Art Nouveau grandeur in Splendid Palas Hotel Istanbul as you walk through their luxuriously designed interiors with rooms facing the city or the Marmara Sea. You'll be left wondering if you traveled back in time during your stay, but that's the charm of this beautiful hotel! 🇹🇷

If you're the type to incorporate a little history in your trips, the hotel itself is full of colorful anecdotes and stories spanning decades. Feel free to ask the staff and connect with the locals about this 111-year old icon! ❤️

Are you a fan of Art Nouveau design and architecture? Would you consider staying here? 😍
 
📸 @admbrs
📍 @splendidpalasbuyukada, Istanbul, Turkey
